overview: This site is the personal yacht sales website of Steve Fill, the senior broker at Bradford Marine Yacht Sales. A graduate of the College of William and Mary, Steve is an innovator who excels at, and takes pride in his client service, always putting listening to a clients wishes and desires at the top of his list. His talent in using creativity to develop win-win solutions to satisfy both parties when putting deals together has contributed immensely to his success. Steve is also a member of the Florida Yacht Brokers Association with whom he regularly attends continuing education seminars so he is always at the forefront of the rules and regulations of his profession.
